                            <p>We are checking that an account is the authentic presence of the public figure, celebrity or global brand it represents.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="info">
                            <div class="icon icon-danger">
                                <i class="material-icons">email</i>
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="info-title">Verified Email Address</h4>
                            <p>Using a online tool to check either entered email adress is Valid or not and if that email adress is not Registered yet.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section text-center">
